Sentence: Because she (priestess) released Ser Jaime Lannister, her (priestess) family's sworn enemy, without the permission of her (priestess) son Robb, the King in the North, Lady Catelyn Stark is accused of treason
Ser Jaime Lannister, meanwhile, is on his (Lannister) way back to King's Landing after being released by Catelyn Stark
When Jaime returns to the House of Lannister, he (Jaime) is restored to the Kingsguard and has a dramatic change of heart about himself
